00:35:18.130 --> 00:35:22.900
so many important commissions,
so many important performances,

00:35:22.900 --> 00:35:27.020
etc. Etc. so what we thought we
would do is put together a little

00:35:27.020 --> 00:35:30.320
display and we have
done that for you today,

00:35:30.320 --> 00:35:32.570
featuring just a couple
of those stories.

00:35:32.570 --> 00:35:35.530
So, what I'll do is I'll run
through a couple of those stories

00:35:35.530 --> 00:35:37.020 position:56%
that we did not tell in the exhibit.

00:35:37.020 --> 00:35:42.260 position:56%
And then I think we'll have a little
bit of time for questions for me,

00:35:42.260 --> 00:35:45.890
Robin and Margery and we'd
love for you to come up

00:35:45.890 --> 00:35:47.580
